children.label: registerFeatures
description:
Register features to be used by the elastic assistant.

Note: Be sure to use the pluginName that is sent in the request headers by your plugin to ensure it is extracted
and the correct features are available. See {@link getPluginNameFromRequest} for more details.

children.label: pluginName
description: Name of the plugin the features should be registered to

children.label: features
description: Partial<AssistantFeatures> to be registered with for the given plugin

children.label: getRegisteredFeatures
description: Get the registered features for a given plugin name.

children.label: pluginName
description: Name of the plugin to get the features for

children.label: registerTools
description:
Register tools to be used by the elastic assistant.

Note: Be sure to use the pluginName that is sent in the request headers by your plugin to ensure it is extracted
and the correct tools are selected. See {@link getPluginNameFromRequest} for more details.

children.label: pluginName
description: Name of the plugin the tool should be registered to

children.label: tools
description: AssistantTools to be registered with for the given plugin

children.label: getRegisteredTools
description: Get the registered tools for a given plugin name.

children.label: pluginName
description: Name of the plugin to get the tools for

children.label: registerCallback
description: Register a callback to be used by the elastic assistant.
